<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.9">
<l>kampa mākaḷi ṟañci<supplied>k</supplied>ka  laṅkavōr</l>
<l>kompu koṇṭaku raikaḻal kūttaṉai</l>
<l>kompu lāmpoḻil kōṭṭiyūrk kaṇṭupōy</l>
<l>nampa ṉaicceṉṟu kaṇṭunā vāyuḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone and seen the dancer with rattling anklets who took</l>
<l>A tusk to harass a huge, quivering elephant, frightening [it],</l>
<l>In Kōṭṭiyūr, where branches sway in groves,</l>
<l>We will go see the prince in Nāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
